      <title>科技股暴跌可能使 IPO 变得更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/tech-stock-selloff-threatens-to-make-ipos-an-even-harder-sell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于华尔街的投资银行家来说，科技股的持续抛售有可能加剧一个痛苦的现实：投资者并不热衷于参与该行业的下一场大型 IPO。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/tech-stock-selloff-threatens-to-make-ipos-an-even-harder-sell</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:57:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
